        <li>Document opt-in source, message type promised, and maximum weekly frequency per segment.</li>
        <li>Configure quiet hours before enabling automations; audit checkout and popup copy quarterly.</li>
        <li>Assign one owner for reply inbox, suppression maps, and pre-launch TCPA review.</li>
        <li>Measure opt-out rate by flow, cost per incremental order, and full-price repeat purchase quality.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="prose-shopify card mt-8">
      <h2>SMS operations depth 3: cost-per-message modeling including carrier…</h2>
      <p>For <strong>compare brevo vs mailchimp</strong>, cost-per-message modeling including carrier fees and discount depth is not optional infrastructure. Shopify SMS apps that recover urgent revenue without wrecking consent treat every text as a scarce interrupt — cart recovery after meaningful checkout intent, launch access for opted-in VIPs, replenishment when SKU usage data supports timing.</p>
